OL,3,CFamily of woman hit by HGV pay tribute
OL,4,Cto 'loving nanna and mum'
OL,6,FThe family of a woman while crossing
OL,7,Fthe road in Rochdale, have paid
OL,8,Ftribute to a "loving nanna, mum and
OL,9,Ffriend to many".
OL,11,FBrenda Rostron, 63, died while using
OL,12,Fher mobility scooter at a pedestrian
OL,13,Fcrossing on Spotland Road on Thursday,
OL,14,F1 February.JA 32-year-old man arrested
OL,15,Fon suspicion of causing death by
OL,16,Fcareless driving has since been
OL,17,Freleased under investigation, (GMP)
OL,18,Fsaid.JIn the wake of Brenda's death, a
OL,19,Ffundraising page has been launched to
OL,20,Fhelp her heartbroken family with
OL,21,Ffuneral costs.
