OL,6,FIn a tribute, Brenda's family spoke of
OL,7,Fthe 'special memories' they will
OL,8,Ftreasure.JThey also issued a plea to
OL,9,Fsocial media users after images of the
OL,10,Fcollision were shared online.JThe
OL,11,Ffamily said: "Brenda is our mum, she
OL,12,Fis a loving nanna to our children and
OL,13,Fa friend to many. We have had our
OL,14,Fhearts broken at the news of her
OL,15,Fpassing.J"No one should lose someone
OL,16,Fthey love in this way, and all we want
OL,17,Fnow is to be able to grieve as a
OL,18,Ffamily in peace and remember her and
OL,19,Fall the special memories we have of
OL,20,Fher.
