OL,6,F"Seeing that people have been taking
OL,7,Fpictures and circulating them online
OL,8,Fhas hurt us more than we can put into
OL,9,Fwords and it has caused our family
OL,10,Findescribable pain.J"We ask that
OL,11,Fpeople please take these down and do
OL,12,Fnot share any more photos from the
OL,13,Fincident. We just need to be together
OL,14,Fas a family now and grieve in peace."
OL,16,FLaura thanked everyone who has donated
OL,17,Fto and for the support her family has
OL,18,Freceived.JLaura said: "It's hard to
OL,19,Fknow what to say. We are just broken
OL,20,Fas a family.
