OL,4,Cto 'loving nanna and mum'
OL,6,F"She lived for her family, she worked
OL,7,Fso hard raising Ryan and I solo and
OL,8,Fdid an amazing job. She was loved by
OL,9,Fso many people, just reading all the
OL,10,Flovely comments about her on Facebook
OL,11,Fhas been a real comfort.J"As a family
OL,12,Fwe really appreciate everyone's
OL,13,Fsupport and want to say a big thank
OL,14,Fyou to everyone who has donated which
OL,15,Fwill help give mum the send off she
OL,16,Fdeserves."
