OL,6,F"A lot of people were fond of her. She
OL,7,Floved her grandchildren and Laura and
OL,8,Fher brother."JGMP are continuing to
OL,9,Finvestigate the collision. Anyone with
OL,10,Finformation about the incident is
OL,11,Fbeing urged to come forward.JPC Philip
OL,12,FDrummond, of GMP's Serious Collision
OL,13,FInvestigation Unit, said: "This has
OL,14,Fcome as devastating news to Brenda's
OL,15,Ffamily and the images circulating
OL,16,Fonline have caused distress and pain
OL,17,Fto a grieving family.
