OL,6,F"I want to echo their words and ask
OL,7,Fthat any images or footage of this
OL,8,Fincident be taken down.J"We are still
OL,9,Fappealing for information about this
OL,10,Fincident and you should pass any
OL,11,Finformation or footage directly to the
OL,12,Fpolice. You can make a report by
OL,13,Fcalling 0161 856 4741 quoting log 1373
OL,14,Fof February 1, 2024. Alternatively,
OL,15,Fyou can call the independent charity
OL,16,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,17,F111."
